library(Seurat)
library(magrittr)
my.samples <- list()

my.samples[[1]] <- readRDS("~/spinal_cord_paper/data/Gg_D05_ctrl_seurat_060223.rds")
my.samples[[2]] <- readRDS("~/spinal_cord_paper/data/Gg_D07_ctrl_seurat_060223.rds")
my.samples[[3]] <- readRDS("~/spinal_cord_paper/data/Gg_ctrl_1_seurat_060223.rds")

names(my.samples) <- c("Gg_D05_ctrl", "Gg_D07_ctrl", "Gg_ctrl_1")
# integration features
features <- SelectIntegrationFeatures(
    object.list = my.samples,
    nfeatures = 3000
    )

# prepare integration 
my.samples <- PrepSCTIntegration(
    object.list = my.samples,
    anchor.features = features
    )

# find anchors
NT.anchors <- FindIntegrationAnchors(
    object.list = my.samples,
    normalization.method = "SCT",
    anchor.features = features
    )
